headline: Mastercard's Meyer Talks Retail and Travel Trends
summary: Mastercard Economics Institute Chief Economist Michelle Meyer says retailers are still seeing an engaged consumer and there's no clear evidence yet that tariffs are playing a role in spending on "Bloomberg The Close."

headline: UK shoppers owed up to £70 each in MasterCard fee case
summary: Consumers can claim if they lived in England, Wales or Northern Ireland between 1997 and 2008 and shopped at UK businesses accepting Mastercard.
